/usr/share/info/gawk_statist.jpg
```

**Fix:** Add a `%files` line that globs these files. In the appropriate `%files` section (the main `gawk` package section), add:

```
%{_infodir}/gawk_*-figure*.png
%{_infodir}/gawk_*.jpg
```

Or more simply, since all unpackaged files are under `${_infodir}` and match `gawk_*`:

```
%{_infodir}/gawk_*.{png,jpg}
```

This captures the seven missing image files without being overly broad. Place it in the main `%files` section of the spec, alongside the existing `%doc` and `%license` entries.
